{"tid":2091872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名加拿大軍人持大量槍械衝入總理杜魯多住處後被捕","createTime":"2020-07-03T02:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T08:12:36.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d30798510e476f584a20864eb321be0d6121e97e","tid":2091872,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"加拿大一名軍人2日駕駛車輛闖入總督官邸麗都廳（Rideau Hall），總理杜魯道和家人在官邸區內有一處住宅，幸好當時全都不在家，軍人落網被搜出大量槍枝，他供稱自己此行是為了要找杜魯道談話。<br />\n<br />\n據《BBC》報導，嫌犯於2日清晨駕駛自己的黑色皮卡車闖進麗都廳正門，隨後因車輛毀損便下車步行入內，警方於上午8時30分（台灣時間2日晚間8時30分）將其逮捕，現場沒有任何衝突發生。<br />\n<br />\n........<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3216472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3216472&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=5e324b1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3216472&h=eb6b151d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3216472</a>"},{"pid":"c0bae889a417c505daf6dcf9a68b3760117bd1f0","tid":2091872,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6dfd45a137b3a4fa75093ff902a91cf13c2e44","tid":2091872,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:23:13.000Z","msg":"可惜"},{"pid":"89604103794408b8ba9c46134ac8d479e877fec5","tid":2091872,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:26:35.000Z","msg":"總督唔係Trudeau"},{"pid":"c064a4221030c5445186371b7f0226ea5c5086c2","tid":2091872,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"啲items 想運過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac9855df82cd2b3cb4621a55cb0f18a6b604e37","tid":2091872,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89604103794408b8ba9c46134ac8d479e877fec5","tid":2091872,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:26:35.000Z","msg":"總督唔係Trudeau"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:31:55.000Z","msg":"加拿大警方拘捕一名男子，涉嫌持有武器，闖入總理杜魯多位於渥太華的住所範圍。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，這名男子在早上約6時40分，持有武器進入杜魯多官邸的所屬範圍，警方迅即將他拘捕。杜魯多的發言人表示，事發時杜魯多並不在家。<br />\n<br />\n杜魯多與他的家人住在「麗都廳」總督府，總督府位於一個佔地0.35平方公里的樹林莊園內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535493-20200703.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535493-20200703.htm&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=7eb847c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535493-20200703.htm&h=62fba65c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535493-20200703.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n總督府係佢住個個區嘅名?"},{"pid":"998df915bd8b019a51b2f15d9ee43812dd75d153","tid":2091872,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89604103794408b8ba9c46134ac8d479e877fec5","tid":2091872,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:26:35.000Z","msg":"總督唔係Trudeau"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"Mr Trudeau and his family, who are currently living at a cottage on the Rideau Hall estate while the prime minister's official residence is being renovated, were not at home at the time of the incident."},{"pid":"872691a4427b2794cc61ffdc06b4c6e82a833830","tid":2091872,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ac9855df82cd2b3cb4621a55cb0f18a6b604e37","tid":2091872,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89604103794408b8ba9c46134ac8d479e877fec5","tid":2091872,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:26:35.000Z","msg":"總督唔係Trudeau"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim